{"type":null,"faqId":12902,"title":"P7 手机发热量大，如何解决？","answer":"<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span><span style=\"font-family:Wingdings;font-size:8pt;\"><span>l </span></span>手机在充电或使用耗电量大的功能及应用如玩游戏、上网、通话等时发热是普遍现象。</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:Wingdings;font-size:8pt;\"><span>l<span>&nbsp;</span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span>建议在充电时不要进行上网、玩游戏、看视频或通话等高功耗的操作。另外，请在阴凉干燥的地方充电。</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:Wingdings;font-size:8pt;\"><span>l<span>&nbsp;</span></span></span><span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">建议玩游戏时彻底关闭后台暂时不使用的应用程序。玩游戏时，手机</span><span> CPU </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">处于高负载状态，会产生较大热量。</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:Wingdings;font-size:8pt;\"><span>l<span>&nbsp;</span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span>建议尽量在信号强度大的地方使用移动数据业务。另外，请不要同时开启大量第三方应用程序，这样不仅会造成流量突增，同时会增加手机的发热量。</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:Wingdings;font-size:8pt;\"><span>l<span>&nbsp;</span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span>建议尽量在信号强度良好的地方通话。</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">华为会在官网发布最新软件版本，请前往</span><span><a href=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/cn/\">http://consumer.huawei.com/cn/</a> </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">根据型号查询；或通过在线升级进行手机软件版本更新，以获得更好的使用体验。</span></span> \n</p>","faqTypeId":144,"faqType":"其他","useful":6,"unUseful":16,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"3803","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Others","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1400140989000,"seriesProductName":"Sophia-L00,Sophia-L05,Sophia-L07,Sophia-L09","visitedTimes":2220,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":4,"times":1,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"3","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"P7 发热","avgScore":4.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}